name: Zil Shiba Inu
description: Zil Shiba Inu is a cryptocurrency based on the Zilliqa network that was born as a fun and lighthearted initiative in the world of meme coins. Our mission is to provide a unique and exciting experience for the cryptocurrency community by harnessing the power of humor and meme virality. While initially not having a specific purpose, we are committed to building an engaged community and exploring future opportunities for ZShiba
